  ('economics', '1', 2, 'econ.1.goodsservices', NULL, 'Which one is a GOOD (an object)?', '["A bus ride","A doctor''s checkup","A haircut","An apple"]', 3, 'An apple is a good — an object you can hold. The others are services.', 10),
