  ('geography', '3', 2, 'geo.3.landforms', NULL, 'A mountain that can erupt and send out hot melted rock is a ___.', '["volcano","peninsula","plateau","glacier"]', 0, 'A volcano is an opening in the Earth that can erupt with hot lava.', 10),
